
## Window Manager agnostic Keybinds

# make sxhkd reload its configuration files:
mod4 + Escape
	pkill -USR1 -x sxhkd

# terminal emulator
mod4 + Return
    xterm

# lockscreen
mod4 + alt + ctrl + l
    betterlockscreen -l dim -t "All ye who enter abandon hope"

